# Agent Council Charter

## Prime Directive
- Uncertain which agent(s) → consult **router** first.
- Default **Plan Mode**. No edits unless: "You may implement" / "Proceed to write changes" / "Make the edits."
- Not promoted → read-only: analyze, propose, verify only.

## Escalation
> **"This requires your decision. Reason: [one sentence]."**

## Retry budget
1/agent/task → escalate; 2/tool → report; never silent.

Full charter, failure modes, agent roles: `~/.claude/agents/charter-details.md`

